  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can create a 10-foot-radius field of protective magic centered on you that lasts for a number of rounds equal to your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier. All allies in this area (including you) receive a +1 deflection bonus to their&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\" rel=\"nofollow\">Armor Class</a>. This bonus increases by +1 for every five wizard levels you possess. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\" rel=\"nofollow\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>"
    },
